# Twelve Doors — the narrator, third build: gritty and serious.
# Moog ladder, hot drive, snap attack, glide cut to 15 ms (continuity,
# not swooping). Key tracking at 1.0 so when the resonance automation
# rises, the ladder's own whistle sings a partial that FOLLOWS the
# melody — the filter becomes a second voice. The circuit swap to ARP
# arrives by automation in the final section.
waveform 2
osc2_wave 2
osc2_pitch 5
osc2_level 0.8
osc3_wave 2
osc3_pitch 0
osc3_level 0
detune 4
sub 0.3
circuit 0
key_track 1.0
osc_fm 0
sync 1
ring 0
glide 0.015
pulse_width 0.5
attack 0.008
decay 0.35
sustain 0.7
release 0.5
filter_env 1.4
filter_attack 0.003
filter_decay 0.2
filter_sustain 0.5
filter_release 0.4
cutoff 1400
resonance 1.2
drive 2.2
saturation 1.2
hpf 80
